[medium] policies/secretsmanager_privacy_transfer_governance.rego:143 (correctness vs. the actual SDK/library)
When PI transfer region governance is enabled, an Allow principal whose account ID is absent from data.account_id_to_region is skipped entirely. principal_region only returns a value for mapped accounts, so a resource policy granting access to an undocumented cross-account principal such as 999999999999 produces no cross_border_principal_undocumented finding even though the policy description and data table make account_id_to_region the documentation source for principal processing regions.
Suggested fix: Split the check into two cases: emit cross_border_principal_undocumented when an Allow principal has an account ID that is not present in data.account_id_to_region while the map is non-empty, and keep the existing disallowed-region check for mapped accounts whose region is not in data.allowed_pi_transfer_regions. Add tests for an unmapped cross-account principal.
Guidance: Fix policies/secretsmanager_privacy_transfer_governance.rego. The current principal_region helper only returns mapped accounts, so an Allow principal with an unmapped cross-account ID disappears from the cross_border_principal_undocumented rule. Keep the existing mapped-region case, but add a second violation case for unmapped cross-account principals when count(data.account_id_to_region) > 0. The new case must require resource_type == "secret", is_pi_secret, resource_policy_present, principal := principals[_], allow_effect(principal), principal_account := principal_account_id(principal), principal_account != account_id, and object.get(data.account_id_to_region, principal_account, "") == "". Reuse the existing violation id "cross_border_principal_undocumented". Do not flag same-account principals just because the local account is absent from the map. Do not remove the existing allowed_pi_transfer_regions check for mapped accounts. Add tests in policies/secretsmanager_privacy_transfer_governance_test.rego for an Allow bare-account or ARN cross-account principal absent from data.account_id_to_region that triggers the finding, and a same-account unmapped principal that does not.
